doctype html
html
  head
    title Adventure Dashboard
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/css/game-player.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css")
    script(src="https://unpkg.com/html5-qrcode")
  body
    .layout-container
      nav.sidebar-container
        .nav-group
          a.nav-link.active(href="#")
            i.fas.fa-home
            span HOME
          a.nav-link(href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="openBag()")
            i.fas.fa-briefcase
            span BAG

      main.main-display-container
        .media-background
          img(src="/images/round1.png") 

        .status-header-overlay
          .status-pill
            .stat-item
              span.icon ★
              span.label Treasures: 0
            .divider
            .stat-item
              span.icon ✪
              span.label Coins: #{player.coins}

        .hero-box(style="z-index: 100;") 
          .info-glass-card
            .info-row
              label CURRENT ROUND
              span.value-text= room.round_number
            .info-row
              label PLAYER NAME
              span.value-text= player.player_name
            
            hr(style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(216, 181, 106, 0.2); margin: 15px 0;")

            .interaction-zone
              .mobile-only(style="display: none;")
                button.btn-pill.btn-scan(type="button" style="cursor: pointer;")
                  i.fas.fa-qrcode 
                  |  SCAN QR CODE
                p.hint-text(style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #D8B56A; margin-top: 8px; opacity: 0.8;") Scan physical qr code to next page 

              .desktop-only(style="display: none;")
                p(style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #D8B56A; margin-bottom: 10px;") Manual Entry Mode
                .manual-input-group(style="display: flex; gap: 10px;")
                  input#manualCell.btn-pill(type="text" placeholder="CELL (C03)" style="width: 50%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(216, 181, 106, 0.3); color: white;")
                  input#manualVerify.btn-pill(type="text" placeholder="CODE" style="width: 50%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(216, 181, 106, 0.3); color: white;")
                button#manualSubmit.btn-pill(style="margin-top: 15px; background: #D8B56A; color: #000; font-weight: bold; width: 100%;") 
                  i.fas.fa-unlock-alt
                  |  UNLOCK CELL

        button.rules-btn(onclick="openRules()") Rule of Game

    //- --- RULES MODAL START ---
    #rules-modal.bag-overlay(style="display: none;")
      .bag-container(style="max-width: 500px; height: 75vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column;")
        .bag-tabs
          button.tab-btn.active RULE OF THE GAMES
        
        .rules-scroll-area(style="padding: 20px; color: #eee; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; overflow-y: auto; flex: 1;")
          h2(style="text-align:center; color:#D8B56A; border-bottom:2px solid #D8B56A; padding-bottom:15px; text-transform: uppercase;") 📜 Rule of the Games

          section(style="margin-bottom: 25px;")
            h3(style="color:#D8B56A;") 🎲 1. MOVEMENT & SCANNING
            p Roll **2 Dice** to move your character on the physical map. Once you land on a cell, click **SCAN QR** on your dashboard. After a successful scan, approach the **Host** to receive your **Physical Card** or rewards.

          section(style="margin-bottom: 25px;")
            h3(style="color:#f39c12;") ⚔️ 2. QUESTION CHALLENGE (RD 2, 4, 6)
            p At the start of these rounds, you must complete a **3-Question Challenge**. Choose your difficulty:
            ul(style="list-style: none; padding-left: 10px;")
              li 🟢 **Easy Mode**: Lower difficulty, smaller rewards.
              li 🔴 **Challenge Mode**: Higher difficulty, massive rewards.
            p *After finishing the questions, you will return to the dashboard to continue your physical move and scan Shop or Special cells.*

          section(style="margin-bottom: 25px;")
            h3(style="color:#D8B56A;") 💰 3. THE SHOP (TRADING POST)
            p Scanning a Shop cell allows you to enter the trading interface **without answering any questions**. You can spend your **Coins** here to buy item cards. Remember to collect your physical cards from the Host after purchase.

          section(style="margin-bottom: 25px;")
            h3(style="color:#D8B56A;") 🌟 4. SPECIAL CELLS
            p These cells are locked by riddles. After scanning, you must answer a **Question** to unlock the rewards. 
            ul(style="list-style: none; padding-left: 10px;")
              li ✅ **Correct**: Receive Coins and random Physical Cards.
              li ❌ **Wrong**: The cell stays locked and **nothing happens** for this turn.

          section(style="margin-bottom: 25px;")
            h3(style="color:#D8B56A;") 🎴 5. CARD MANUAL (ITEMS)
            //- Added color: #2F4F4F to the card-item containers
            .card-item(style="background:rgba(216, 181, 106, 0.15); padding:10px; border-radius:5px; margin-bottom:10px; border-left: 3px solid #D8B56A; color: #2F4F4F;")
              strong(style="color: #2F4F4F;") 🔍 Verify Card: 
              | Use only in **Rd 5 & 7**. Give the card and a **Treasure ID** to the Host. The Host signals **1 for REAL** or **0 for FAKE**.
            
            .card-item(style="background:rgba(216, 181, 106, 0.15); padding:10px; border-radius:5px; margin-bottom:10px; border-left: 3px solid #D8B56A; color: #2F4F4F;")
              strong(style="color: #2F4F4F;") 🥾 Movement Card: 
              | Show to the Host **before rolling the dice** to add extra steps to your total movement.

          section(style="margin-bottom: 25px;")
            h3(style="color:#D8B56A;") 🏆 6. WINNING CONDITIONS
            p The winner is the player with the **Most Real Treasures**. 
            p *In the event of a tie, the player with the highest **Total Coins** will be declared the winner.*
        
        .bag-footer
          button.exit-btn(onclick="closeRules()") Exit

    #bag-modal.bag-overlay(style="display: none;")
      .bag-container
        .bag-tabs
          button.tab-btn.active(onclick="switchTab('cards')") My Cards
          button.tab-btn(onclick="switchTab('clues')") My Clues
          button.tab-btn(onclick="switchTab('treasures')") My Treasure
        
        .bag-content
          #bag-grid.bag-grid
          
        .bag-footer
          button.exit-btn(onclick="closeBag()") Exit

    #qr-reader-container(style="display:none; position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.9); z-index:10000; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center;")
      #qr-reader(style="width: 300px; background: white; border: 2px solid #D8B56A;")
      button#close-scanner.btn-pill(style="margin-top: 20px; background: #666; cursor: pointer;") CLOSE

    script.
      const SESSION_ID = "#{room.session_id}";
      const MY_PLAYER_NAME = "#{player.player_name}";
      const ROOM_ACCESS_CODE = "#{room.session_access_code}";

      function openRules() {
        document.getElementById('rules-modal').style.display = 'flex';
      }
      function closeRules() {
        document.getElementById('rules-modal').style.display = 'none';
      }

    script(src="/js/game-player.js")